snippet.title: Ray Fisher Let's Talk Accountability of Zack Snyder's Justice League & Ben Affleck, Amber, Ezra...
snippet.description:
Okay Ray Fisher... lets talk Accountability being Greater than Entertainment... do you really mean it? Or do you mean all entertainment except Zack Snyder's Justice League? Because if we're being honest, one could STILL call the behavior of many of your cast mates, the same things you're leveling at Joss Whedon and Walter Hamada.... Ben Affleck, Ezra Miller, Amber Heard, Jason Momoa even Jared Leto all have done wrong. What kind of accountability do you require? Is an apology tweet enough?
